## 1.2 First Trades

```
🟢 Easy · ⏱ Week 2-4 · 💰 ₹10,000-15,000
```

**What it is:** Your first actual buying and selling of scrap metal. You go to the market with ₹10,000 cash, buy one metal you understand well (copper recommended), sort it at home, and sell to a buyer at higher price. Repeat with increasing amounts.

**Why this step matters:** Theory becomes reality. You experience actual negotiation, quality checking, transport logistics, and cash flow management. Each trade makes you smarter. The profit is small initially but the learning is massive.

**How to do it — Trade by Trade:**

| Trade # | Buy What | Buy Price | Quantity | Total Cost | Sell Price | Revenue | Profit | Time |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
