## 1.3 Scale Trading

```
🟢 Easy · ⏱ Month 2-3 · 💰 ₹30,000-80,000 working capital
```

**What it is:** You increase trade size from 15-30 kg to 100-500 kg. You add inter-city arbitrage — buying in your city where prices are low, selling in another city where prices are high. You hire one helper and rent a small storage space.

**Why this step matters:** Small trades (₹10,000-20,000) earn ₹1,000-3,000 each. Bigger trades (₹50,000-2,00,000) earn ₹5,000-25,000 each with the SAME amount of effort. Scaling trade size is how you go from ₹30,000/month to ₹1-2 lakh/month.

**Inter-city arbitrage — how it works:**

| You Buy In | Price | You Sell In | Price | Transport Cost (500 kg) | Profit Per Trade |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Hyderabad (copper ₹610/kg) | ₹3,05,000 | Chennai (₹670/kg) | ₹3,35,000 | ₹5,000 | ₹25,000 |
| Delhi (aluminum ₹155/kg) | ₹77,500 | Jaipur (₹185/kg) | ₹92,500 | ₹3,000 | ₹12,000 |
| Ahmedabad (brass ₹360/kg) | ₹1,08,000 | Mumbai (₹410/kg) | ₹1,23,000 | ₹4,000 | ₹11,000 |

**How to find price differences between cities:**
- WhatsApp trading groups post prices from multiple cities daily
- IndiaMART shows buy/sell prices by location
- Call 2-3 dealers in different cities every morning and note prices
- MCX futures show national trend — local markets lag by 1-2 days

**Monthly revenue progression:**

| Month | Avg Trade Size | Trades/Month | Avg Profit/Trade | Monthly Profit |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Month 1 | ₹10,000-15,000 | 6-8 | ₹1,000-1,500 | ₹8,000-12,000 |
| Month 2 | ₹30,000-50,000 | 8-12 | ₹3,000-5,000 | ₹30,000-60,000 |
| Month 3 | ₹50,000-2,00,000 | 10-15 | ₹5,000-15,000 | ₹60,000-1,50,000 |

**Expenses at this stage:**

| Expense | Monthly Cost | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Helper (1 person) | ₹8,000-10,000 | Loading, sorting, transport assistance |
| Godown/storage rent | ₹5,000-15,000 | Small shed 200-500 sq ft in industrial area |
| Transport (tempo hire) | ₹5,000-15,000 | Porter/local tempo for deliveries |
| Phone/internet | ₹500-1,000 | Calls to dealers and buyers |
| **TOTAL** | **₹18,500-41,000** | |

**Common mistake:** Not tracking MCX (Multi Commodity Exchange) prices daily. Download the MCX app. Check copper, aluminum, and lead futures every morning. If MCX copper drops 3 percent today, scrap market copper drops tomorrow — because street markets react 1-2 days late. Buy BEFORE the drop reaches the street. Sell BEFORE a rise is priced in. This information advantage is free and gives you guaranteed extra margin.

**One-liner:** Same effort per trade, bigger quantity = bigger profit. Scale your trade size, not your number of trades.

**Checklist:**
```
✅ Working capital above ₹50,000
✅ Doing 100+ kg trades regularly
✅ Completed at least 1 inter-city trade
✅ Hired 1 helper
✅ Rented small storage space
✅ Checking MCX prices every morning
✅ Monthly profit crossed ₹50,000
✅ Have 15+ suppliers and 8+ buyers in phone contacts
```

