**Why this step matters:** This is the bridge from general scrap trader to e-waste specialist. Electronic scrap teaches you what valuable metals (gold, silver, palladium, copper) are hiding inside electronics. This knowledge is the foundation of Phase 2, 3, 4, and the entire empire.

