| 3 | Send LinkedIn message | "We are SPCB-authorized e-waste collector in [city]. Processing [X] tons/month. Can support your EPR targets in [state]. Attached: our authorization. Would you like to discuss?" |
| 4 | Follow up on email | If they respond, send formal proposal with: capacity, coverage area, pricing, certificate format |
| 5 | Sign agreement | Standard EPR collection agreement (they usually have a template) |

