| Brand Category | Typical Volume Given | Rate/kg | Monthly Income |
|---|---|---|---|
| Smartphone brand (Samsung, Xiaomi) | 500-2,000 kg/month | ₹15-25/kg | ₹7,500-50,000 |
| Computer brand (HP, Dell, Lenovo) | 1,000-5,000 kg/month | ₹10-20/kg | ₹10,000-1,00,000 |
| Appliance brand (LG, Samsung, Whirlpool) | 2,000-10,000 kg/month | ₹8-15/kg | ₹16,000-1,50,000 |

**With 2-4 brand partnerships: ₹50,000-3,00,000/month additional income.**

**Simultaneously — disposal certificates for local businesses:**

| Client Type | What They Need | What You Charge | Your Volume |
